---
title: Chicken and Spinach Pasta with Cream Cheese
description: Creamy, cheesy pasta, yes please!!! Drop the fusilli in boiling water, leave the juicy seasoned chicken breasts to roast, and put your feet up. Dinner will be done before you can say onomatopoeia!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-and-spinach-pasta-324055d5.jpg
